name: Movieman
0:

”Alexa open movie man and give me information about thor”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: movie man
des: Movieman skill can be used to get all information about any movie of your choice. It tells you exact release dates to all movies, It's Directors' names, Actors who performed in that movie, Languages in which the movie is available, IMDB, Rotten Tomatoes and other ratings, the Genre of the movie. Basically it is the encyclopedia of movies.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
